328
00:24:14,060 --> 00:24:15,799
- I'm not leaving.
- Don't touch my mom!

329
00:24:15,799 --> 00:24:18,480
He Wei Fang, your mother did not die of illness.

330
00:24:18,480 --> 00:24:20,120
Wait a moment.

331
00:24:22,640 --> 00:24:24,372
What did you say?

332
00:24:26,000 --> 00:24:31,900
