and the sick outside the city.

372
00:26:56,820 --> 00:26:58,659
There's nothing unusual on ordinary days.

373
00:26:58,659 --> 00:27:00,699
The surrounding neighbors praise him highly.

374
00:27:00,699 --> 00:27:04,419
They say he is kind and approachable,
and very good with children.

375
00:27:04,419 --> 00:27:06,580
Do you have his portrait?

376
00:27:28,979 --> 00:27:30,976
Mu Dan.

377
00:27:32,879 --> 00:27:35,100
Ms. He, you're here.

378
00:27:35,100 --> 00:27:38,440
It's cold outside.
Come in and warm yourself by the fire.

379
00:27:38,440 --> 00:27:42,860
No need. I have something to ask you.

380
00:27:42,860 --> 00:27:45,000
Could you please come out for a moment?

381
00:27:46,820 --> 00:27:50,739
Kang, continue to read the legend with them.

382
00:27:50,739 --> 00:27:52,368
Alright.

383
00:28:16,380 --> 00:28:21,300
Is your real name Wu Hong?

384
00:28:22,659 --> 00:28:24,404
Yes.

385
00:28:26,219 --> 00:28:31,640
Do you know the owner
of the He's Pharmacy in Luoyang?

386
00:28:33,079 --> 00:28:34,780
I do.

387
00:28:39,219 --> 00:28:46,039
You poisoned and killed my mother, right?

388
00:28:49,300 --> 00:28:52,240
- I did. 
 - Why?

389
00:28:57,380 --> 00:28:59,350
That year,

390
00:29:00,900 --> 00:29:04,180
it wasn't just your mother who died.

391
00:29:05,799 --> 00:29:10,939
That year, I learned that my home
had suffered from a flood.

392
00:29:10,939 --> 00:29:16,179
So I hurried back to Luoyang
and experienced the major post-disaster epidemic.

393
00:29:17,979 --> 00:29:20,639
I watched with open eyes

394
00:29:21,419 --> 00:29:25,672
my parents, wife, and children

395
00:29:27,200 --> 00:29:29,804
die in front of me.

396
00:29:30,739 --> 00:29:36,179
Have you ever experienced
the despair of losing all your loved ones?

397
00:29:36,179 --> 00:29:39,140
But what does this have to do with my mother?

398
00:29:39,140 --> 00:29:42,839
It was poor people like us
who died from the flood.

399
00:29:44,140 --> 00:29:48,140
It was also poor people like us
who died from the plague.

400
00:29:48,140 --> 00:29:53,259
Those officials and wealthy businessmen
all hid in their houses to avoid the plague.

401
00:29:53,259 --> 00:29:55,340
Even if they get sick,
they have money to buy medicine.

402
00:29:55,340 --> 00:29:57,340
But what about us?

403
00:29:58,100 --> 00:30:02,580
People like us can only wait for death.

404
00:30:02,580 --> 00:30:05,160
How can I not hate them?

405
00:30:06,179 --> 00:30:11,179
Do you know, the one who died in my arms last

406
00:30:12,519 --> 00:30:16,119
was my child who hadn't even become 15.

407
00:30:16,960 --> 00:30:21,900
She passed away with her eyes wide open,
unable to die at peace.

408
00:30:23,979 --> 00:30:27,599
At that time, I was filled with hatred.

409
00:30:28,759 --> 00:30:33,380
I just wanted to find someone
to accompany my family to the grave.

410
00:30:34,459 --> 00:30:38,860
But how could I easily enter
those noble and wealthy households?

411
00:30:38,860 --> 00:30:44,240
I roamed everywhere
and finally found an opportunity.

412
00:30:45,200 --> 00:30:48,860
I entered a house.

413
00:30:50,860 --> 00:30:57,079
 Your mother recognized that I was not
the usual farmer who delivered vegetables. 

414
00:30:58,212 --> 00:31:00,224
 So I told her 

415
00:31:00,224 --> 00:31:04,820
 my family members had all died,
and I had no money for their burial. 

416
00:31:04,820 --> 00:31:08,259
 That's why I found this job. 

417
00:31:09,540 --> 00:31:12,620
 She then gave me two strings of coins. 

418
00:31:13,499 --> 00:31:15,659
 I didn't need her charity. 

419
00:31:15,659 --> 00:31:19,159
 I also didn't need her to pretend
to be a good person to me. 

420
00:31:20,699 --> 00:31:24,419
 I just want her to accompany my family in burial. 

421
00:31:40,699 --> 00:31:43,119
Your whole family died.

422
00:31:44,179 --> 00:31:47,939
