434
00:32:37,599 --> 00:32:39,484
You knew.

435
00:32:42,640 --> 00:32:44,659
Why didn't you tell me?

436
00:32:45,920 --> 00:32:48,079
Why didn't you?

437
00:32:48,620 --> 00:32:51,060
When will the cycle of vengeance end?

438
00:32:51,820 --> 00:32:56,699
