short-handed right now.

491
00:39:49,139 --> 00:39:51,139
I want to go and help out.

492
00:39:51,760 --> 00:39:55,459
After the flood,
there are many sick people in the city.

493
00:39:55,459 --> 00:39:59,419
Your father told us not to go out these days.

494
00:40:00,700 --> 00:40:04,499
But with so many patients now,
they surely need someone to take care of them.

495
00:40:04,499 --> 00:40:08,139
And yet here I am, resting easy at home.

496
00:40:08,139 --> 00:40:10,760
I feel very uneasy.

497
00:40:13,539 --> 00:40:17,539
Now, there are many patients
and few medicinal supplies.

498
00:40:17,539 --> 00:40:20,820
If you catch the disease,
you'll take up an extra dose of medicine.

499
00:40:20,820 --> 00:40:24,220
And then other patients will be short one dose.

500
00:40:24,220 --> 00:40:27,260
Moreover, these medicinal packets we're making

501
00:40:27,260 --> 00:40:30,760
can also contribute to the sick people.

502
00:40:32,220 --> 00:40:34,380
Mom, you are right.

503
00:40:34,380 --> 00:40:37,820
However, Mom, is this epidemic really that severe?

504
00:40:37,820 --> 00:40:41,419
Under normal circumstances, it's enough
to use ordinary peonies for medicine.

505
00:40:41,419 --> 00:40:43,419
This time we are using ice crystal peonies.

506
00:40:43,419 --> 00:40:46,440
The flowers in the courtyard
are almost picked clean.

507
00:40:47,000 --> 00:40:51,700
The root and bark of this flower can clear heat,
cool the blood, and alleviate various pains.

508
00:40:51,700 --> 00:40:54,700
Combined with anemarrhena, phellodendron,
and rehmannia for medicine,

509
00:40:54,700 --> 00:40:56,800
it can relieve lung heat.

510
00:40:56,800 --> 00:40:59,740
It is exactly the medicine
most needed for this epidemic.

511
00:40:59,740 --> 00:41:01,764
The ice crystal peonies we have

512
00:41:01,764 --> 00:41:05,059
are the rarest and most hard
to find over vast distances.

513
00:41:05,059 --> 00:41:10,099
In these times of disaster,
one of these is worth a fortune.

514
00:41:14,499 --> 00:41:20,499
Mom, you distribute such valuable materials
to the victims who can't afford treatment.

515
00:41:20,499 --> 00:41:22,499
Mom, you are so kind.

516
00:41:23,260 --> 00:41:26,340
Stamping the auspicious clouds from heaven
on the medicinal packet

517
00:41:26,340 --> 00:41:28,340
also serves to convey blessings.

518
00:41:28,340 --> 00:41:30,700
Hopefully, those who take this medicine

519
00:41:30,700 --> 00:41:34,579
can safely get through this ordeal
and stay healthy.

